=== File methods seek#2 with SEEK_CUR and SEEK_END =============================

file                        -> File
file.tell()                 -> 0
file.seek(5,File.SEEK_SET)  -> File
file.tell()                 -> 5
file.seek(3,File.SEEK_CUR)  -> File
file.tell()                 -> 8
file.seek(0,File.SEEK_END)  -> File
file.tell()                 -> 26

=== File built in constants ====================================================

File.stdin:     File
File.stdout:    File
File.stderr:    File
File.SEEK_SET:  0
File.SEEK_CUR:  1
File.SEEK_END:  2

